            "id": 6010004,
            "title": "智邦5月業績亮眼獲外資點讚 看好AI需求再喊加碼",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>網通股智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>) 受惠 AI 需求強勁，5 月業績再創高，美系外資針對智邦發布最新研究報告，表示智邦在 AI 加速模組與網路交換器訂單需求強勁下，第二季營收可望優於市場預期，並維持加碼評等。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010004%2Fl%2Fee49040f59551b745052f6e2c627e439.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">智邦5月業績亮眼獲外資點讚 看好AI需求再喊加碼。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人表示，智邦 2025 年在 AI 加速器放量、800G 網路交換器規格升級，以及來自另一家超大型雲端客戶的新需求動能，可望持續成長，且智邦與主要客戶維持穩健的合作關係，並擁有強大的系統設計與測試整合能力。核心競爭力在 AI 浪潮下仍具吸引力。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>智邦 5 月營收達<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a> 182.8 億元，月增 3%，年增 108%，連續三個月創新高；累計前 5 月營收 788.12 億元，年增 127.5%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人預估，智邦第二季營收將達 499.63 億元，季增 17%，年增 105%，第二季累計營收已達外資預估的 72%，維持加碼評等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>產品布局上，智邦在資料中心升級需求下，800G 產品出貨暢旺，最新型 1.6T 交換器目前由客戶驗證中。市場預期最晚於明年上半年出貨，有望成為新的營收成長引擎。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
